# A minimal shiny weather dashboard

## Overview
This dashboard uses the [openweathermap](https://openweathermap.org/api) API to get current weather conditions as well as a 5 day forecast for a specific location.

## API usage guide
https://openweathermap.org/appid#work

## Setup
- get and API key (just regist)
- change the coordinates to your location

## API key
To get an API key simply register on t



## Coordinates
https://openweathermap.org/find?q=
